	<string>Emoji Picker

Trigger with the ⌃⌘Space hotkey, or type the `:` keyword, then a search term.
Alfred filters the full emoji list by name, :shortcode:, and keyword.

  Enter  paste the emoji into the front app
  ⌘      copy the :shortcode: instead
  ⌥      copy the emoji without pasting

Data: github/gemoji (see the project Makefile for the pinned version).</string>
